    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The second epoch of the Quaternary and the most recent geologic interval of time. It extends from about 10,000 BCE to the present. It coincides with the late and post-Stone Age history of the human species.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
